---

<Layout title="About — Ben Barnes" description="About Ben Barnes.">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="about">
      <div class="about-portrait">
        <div class="portrait">
          <span>Portrait</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-body">
        <h1 class="about-name">Ben Barnes</h1>
        <p>I live in Atlanta and take photographs wherever I end up. Most of what&rsquo;s here is shot on film &mdash; trips through Europe, weddings and weekends with friends, and the ordinary days in between.</p>
        <p>This site is mostly a place to keep those rolls together. If a frame stops you, that&rsquo;s the whole idea.</p>
        <p class="about-note">&mdash; placeholder bio, swap in your own.</p>

        <div class="about-also">
          <div class="idx-sub" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">Also</div>
          <ul class="also-list">
            <li><a href="/running">Running</a> &mdash; a log of races, PRs, and the occasional DNF.</li>
            <li><a href="/sauna">The sauna</a> &mdash; a backyard build, with photos and a full cost breakdown.</li>
            <li><a href="https://instagram.com/benjaminbarnes" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a> &mdash; newer frames, more often.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
